title: Hour 3 - Paul Tesori (06-25-20)
itunes:title: Hour 3 - Paul Tesori (06-25-20)
description:
Paul Tesori; the caddie for Web Simpson explains to Dan how he learned about golfers testing positive for the corona virus. Paul tells Dan that they are tested usually on Tuesday and Wednesday and then again on Saturdays.
